Columbus Bar Association v. White.

[Cite as Columbus Bar Assn. v. White (1988), 36 Ohio St. 3d 611.]

(D.D. No. 88-2 Decided April 20, 1988.)

Albert M. White, Jr. is publicly reprimanded.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Holmes, Douglas, Jones and H. Brown, JJ., concur. Jones, J., of the Twelfth Appellate District, sitting for Wright, J.
